    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next chapter? This car is in fair condition and offers a solid foundation for anyone seeking a dependable vehicle at a great price! While it shows some honest signs of use and could use a little cosmetic or mechanical attention to truly shine, it\u2019s a fantastic opportunity to own a quality car without the premium price tag. Perfect for someone who appreciates a vehicle with character and potential!",
      "price": 21000.0,
