    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, presenting in showroom condition as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free of any swirls, chips, or imperfections, and has been protected in a climate-controlled environment. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear, and the original factory scent is still present. Every electronic component and mechanical system functions flawlessly, backed by a comprehensive folder of service records and preventative maintenance. From the pristine, dust-free engine bay to the unmarked alloy wheels wrapped in fresh rubber, this car represents the pinnacle of its model. This is a rare opportunity for a buyer who demands perfection and a turn-key driving experience.",
      "price": 47250.0,
